{"title":"- Derroche en salud-2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Gestión en salud/- Derroche en salud-2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Derroche\\Nen salud","guid":"k63XcmAdyI5JCZjT1iH5rQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"1. Resumen","guid":"iAT40n0BrWSLs3r-8zFirg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Aumento gasto salud → búsqueda eficiencia","guid":"YT1BN2uuFmkZlh45INUfFQ","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Concepto wasteful = derroche","guid":"0RbSx39tcUXMujoaKmsOrA","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Principales dominios: prestaciones de bajo valor,\\Nfallas en prestación, fallas en coordinación","guid":"EuqFnTFUJ7guFzfDUDo04A","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"• Procedimientos, diagnósticos,\\Nmedicamentos ineficientes =\\Npreocupación transversal","guid":"ZdNdvKjEWWWnsgOSZiAckw","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"• Recomendación para países de ingresos\\Nmedios/bajos → cuantificar derroche y\\Nmejorar asignación de recursos","guid":"in2PZrTT_SVfIGK6m9DXZA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"• Caso Chile → urgencia en implementar\\Nestrategias para mitigar derroche","guid":"uaH1BOuf1mz_-SHGNTabMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"2. Antecedentes","guid":"6vUwvEJu0sMjNsxmN6H4Fw","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"• Contexto del aumento del\\Ngasto en salud global","guid":"-b7IgaczwWmDK_Yj4fq6pg","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"• Necesidad de eficiencia en\\Nla gestión de recursos","guid":"NuZHxw63CDfxCEvwEfnpeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Antecedentes","guid":"rBuyxNeHXx3I3QPwMxjMdg","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"• Aumento sostenido del gasto en salud\\N(últimas 2 décadas)","guid":"BIQ4Blr1n_tUXt-NjS-6UQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"• Causas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• Complejidad estructural de los sistemas de salud","guid":"Nq83f6zt5c1cNIETPUrLsw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• Innovación tecnológica","guid":"8E8DKoLjzctmyKn_3iouYw","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"13","text":"• Mayor demanda (envejecimiento poblacional, cambios epidemiológicos)","guid":"LFcdyx4qXPF5H-h5fJ7D9A","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"13","text":"• Estrategias de contención de costos (influenciadas por: sistemas políticos, teorías organizacionales, políticas sanitarias)","guid":"seEG5cCvL6U90XCSkcfOOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"11","text":"• Derroche en el gasto\\Nen salud (wasteful)","guid":"","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Definición:","guid":"PXOE9e0dKNY1Q4PMsieHgA","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"• Servicios con poco o ningún beneficio","guid":"tdUCqYw1GlMOUWmZ5JAYQw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"• Falta de evidencia en costo-efectividad","guid":"eHP2JD-9C3WK8kdC-oaeEQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"• Ineficiencias en la provisión de servicios","guid":"lqcAEyQK3w8Z9hXwulRBRg","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"19","text":"• Gastos por condiciones evitables/prevenibles\\N(ej. hospitalizaciones innecesarias)","guid":"4EC5Wg-bEG0BbLZvkXI68Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"11","text":"• Estimaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"• 25% del gasto total en países OCDE (OCDE 2019)","guid":"29a7ac02gHxHYDz5YnPpaQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"• 50% en EE.UU. (Institute 2008)","guid":"GcQRuA5X3oF0mIU6I7cu4Q","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"• EE.UU.: $760-$935 mil millones USD (Shrank et al., 2019)","guid":"eZjE4bUXHcRjdZ829iz-ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"28","parent":"11","text":"• Propuesta de dominios de derroche (Instituto de\\NMedicina de EE.UU., 2010; Berwick y Hackbarth, 2012)","guid":"na38UUocXOzP6aUzv8CHTA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"1. Falla en prestación de servicios","guid":"vX5uX_T7WhpYP2pg_SLLnw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"2. Falla en coordinación de la atención","guid":"Y9oIo819-6FOeyh8jahNjw","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"3. Sobre-tratamiento/atención de bajo valor","guid":"vKDWclcoXLniw0IurJoqqg","children":[]},{"id":"32","parent":"28","text":"4. Falla en precios","guid":"mZ4LGhRT0Yq0m8AckGRrig","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"28","text":"5. Fraude y abuso","guid":"JksPB_utkrftZfXRohELmw","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"28","text":"6. Complejidad administrativa","guid":"ATgJOpyQuBeM8sddBuLlJg","children":[]}]},{"id":"35","parent":"11","text":"• Envejecimiento poblacional → imperativo ético","guid":"N6N6t7BYBGtlIGXhTMYe2w","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"11","text":"• Urgencia en solucionar derroche para eficiencia y equidad (BID, 2018)","guid":"Wz73JcIyz4JpmhC96pvUEA","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"11","text":"• Soluciones\\Nal derroche:","guid":"tuM92nOQxHTUYdjxnK_Q6A","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"• Políticas públicas + cambios en gestión y práctica clínica","guid":"w8FilYWv6FqZD1RpqbC4Pw","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"• Costo-efectividad en procedimientos clínicos","guid":"klv6Scs7_DkrWAblclNcdg","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"• Reducción de costos administrativos","guid":"F-vjGQfJ7_o3mJmBnA7-wQ","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"• Mejorar competencia y regulación de precios\\N(medicamentos/prestaciones)","guid":"JQTjZzDRDPxOrFuyaYwcZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"37","text":"• Incorporación de nuevas tecnologías\\Ny sistemas de información","guid":"k-YNvzDUOhEIRXkjuaKEhg","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"37","text":"• Pago basado en resultados sanitarios\\N(Frakt, 2019)","guid":"JrkMsK5vbRqOwZEEZrm_FA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"0","text":"Marco Conceptual","guid":"AXevydQhki9JDirEk_44pQ","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Objetivo: Evidencia sobre fuentes del derroche en salud\\N+ políticas/estrategias para mitigarlo/eliminarlo.","guid":"2rBuVfb_Rg6uA-8mbmUHIg","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Wasteful → “Derroche”:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Concepto: error evitable en la asignación de recursos\\N(Simpson et al., 1989).","guid":"NbdboOAIL0DRrSf-zo8Tyw","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Homónimo en español = “derroche” →\\Nmalgastar recursos innecesaria/ineficientemente.","guid":"qziy20cpL_Nhvt0jy4Kpvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"44","text":"• 6 dominios de derroche (OIM, 2010;\\NBerwick y Hackbarth, 2012):","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"44","text":"1. Fallos en la prestación\\Nde cuidados (FHC):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"51","parent":"50","text":"• Ej.: fallas en seguridad del paciente, atención preventiva, variabilidad\\Nen atención, uso de hospitales de alto costo, errores médicos.","guid":"ccw0Eu7qANas0PpPPYjA_g","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"50","text":"• Incluye problemas de adherencia a medicamentos.","guid":"K2Q8jR0j9J9ZCze3N0wcCA","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"44","text":"2. Falta de coordinación de\\Nla atención (FCC):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Atención fragmentada → complicaciones, reingresos, deterioro funcional\\N(crónicos → más afectados).","guid":"AfGvwIcZN5Y_RLpL57Trtw","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"44","text":"3. Tratamiento excesivo o de\\Nbajo valor (LOWVAL):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"• Ej.: uso excesivo de antibióticos, cirugías innecesarias,\\Ncuidados intensivos no deseados al final de la vida.","guid":"sHcri1ci6fol59vYupSilQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"44","text":"4. Falla de\\Nprecios (HCPF):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"• Ej.: medicamentos de marca vs genéricos, inflación en\\Nprecios de procedimientos, dispositivos y medicamentos.","guid":"Z3bRQugmmrbueONw3dkn6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"44","text":"5. Fraude y abuso\\N(HCF):","guid":"q_S-dqhbAwctJ7WsSb9kzg","children":[{"id":"60","parent":"59","text":"• Ej.: facturas falsas, fraudes, sobre-regulación por\\Nconductas fraudulentas de pocos prestadores.","guid":"cINJ8m7yXq5rKT97XO7e7w","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"44","text":"6. Complejidad administrativa\\N(HCAC):","guid":"7xV8GEQZKdptWzoVuvTyRg","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"• Ej.: errores de facturación, carga administrativa del médico/seguro,\\Nfalta de estandarización de aranceles/códigos de atención.","guid":"0aUh_VT17U-lftr6M4Ni8A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"63","parent":"0","text":"• Preguntas de\\Ninvestigación:","guid":"0mnjDUT5FNtviOXHEYLYKQ","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"1. ¿Contribución de cada dominio al\\Nderroche en salud (últimos 5 años)?","guid":"TT1NJHfWbUq92OATZVMj0w","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"2. ¿Estrategias/políticas adoptadas\\Npara reducir el derroche?","guid":"DOfiklsPBYpUTTn3qUa_6A","children":[]}]},{"id":"66","parent":"0","text":"4.3 Análisis\\Nnarrativo-sintético:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"67","parent":"66","text":"• FHC (Failures of\\NHealth Care Delivery):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Ineficiencias clínicas (ej. anestésicos, antineoplásicos,\\Nantibióticos, imágenes de diagnóstico).","guid":"8waak1paZGuDybY466suEw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Intervenciones: optimización quirúrgica,\\Nuso de genéricos, incentivos económicos.","guid":"YrylxolwY-TFf5kenKE93Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"66","text":"• FCC (Failures of\\NCare Coordination):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• Fragmentación, reingresos,\\Nhospitalizaciones evitables.","guid":"9VYHK2FnFjQPtcKfQJxmHA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• Intervenciones: atención interdisciplinaria,\\Nintegración de niveles de atención.","guid":"J3mX6udb-4nr27h2Tmvyzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"66","text":"• LOWVAL (Low-value\\NHealth Care):","guid":"joX5KfkEwh4wWD6vISDZGg","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Tratamientos innecesarios e ineficientes\\N(ej. exámenes, medicamentos).","guid":"EnX5peaoeC35AY2wKdnizg","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• Intervenciones: reorganización,\\Nestrategias de Choosing Wisely.","guid":"SxkZnBgnmhWn5mGKL4rkrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"66","text":"• HCPF (Health Care\\NPricing Failure):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Escalada de precios\\N(medicamentos, procedimientos).","guid":"z5Tc2TyYjkh8U2bieD0YIw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• Intervenciones: regulación de\\Nprecios, exenciones de copagos.","guid":"hzN24b__cJ16EeiY3lpfAQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"66","text":"• HCF (Health\\NCare Fraud):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• Fraudes en seguros y\\Nmedicamentos falsificados.","guid":"qu_i_DlfrObVF5Uom1crNg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• Intervenciones: contención de fraudes,\\Nmecanismos a nivel de sistemas de salud.","guid":"Jg8ru82RB3PinAJtmaJ7Zw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"66","text":"• HCAC (Health Care\\NAdministrative Complexity):","guid":"r3kjYWgT6QeaEMJj-vwpKQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Impacto de seguros,\\Nmecanismos de pago ineficientes.","guid":"itG8McQBfeKpHY8IjF7fRg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Intervenciones: pago por desempeño (P4P),\\Norganización de sistemas jerarquizados.","guid":"Y-R9WThClVMZg8LL-lBzxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Discusión","guid":"QkJemDaqXTdtcbeesqgPJA","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Preocupación global por el\\Nderroche en salud:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"• Mayor incremento de estudios en países de altos ingresos\\N(EE.UU., Canadá, Alemania, Australia).","guid":"N0cU6sSK-8ZIxCb8Mx6uJQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"• Urgencia en abordar éticamente la\\Ncontención del gasto en salud.","guid":"kahwCd10-kc9ujyRDl7VbA","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"• Estrategias\\Nimplementadas:","guid":"oiWpz72MZoVrjNgBgLVx4g","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"• Cuantificación del derroche y\\Nmitigación en varios países.","guid":"hjtpRxaAEEf5FriEBU16KQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"• Intervenciones en:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"• Formación de profesionales","guid":"jRHs0rC7Ssd4WL-Wi-UA4Q","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"• Protocolos/guías clínicas","guid":"dqBxeKzQimMtfQwEbPPrYw","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"• Mecanismos de pago","guid":"Lba5xBCM4vu9N488gA0BNg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"• Políticas públicas y regulación","guid":"y77rgFTvFiPRkZuqtU4SBg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"91","text":"• Evaluación de tecnologías sanitarias","guid":"TmqC9LAXKKl1YLBHNsi4yA","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"85","text":"• Tres niveles de gestión en\\Nsalud (OMS 2013):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"1. Micro gestión (relación\\Nprofesional-paciente):","guid":"G-Gc4oZfOCYV8Y4OQ6J7nQ","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Problemas de adherencia a\\Ntratamientos → impacto económico.","guid":"Ew9fZnk3iN-GQaxYLHS_3w","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"• Variabilidad en prácticas clínicas y\\Nuso irracional de recursos.","guid":"fl71yrU9UjyevY0EA807Sw","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"• Propuestas: campañas como Choosing\\NWisely, cambios en currículum de formación.","guid":"9UafriXtcOqDGDtry2v9AQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"2. Meso gestión (eficiencia\\Ntécnica/administrativa, redes\\Nasistenciales):","guid":"8dqtc8ylVbahQcQKPiSiTg","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Fallas en la integración y\\Ncoordinación en redes de salud.","guid":"jsoF6KEaJII2K3Ry-qfpYw","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Propuestas: mejor uso de tecnologías, sistemas\\Nde derivación, gobernanza de redes.","guid":"pEuPRB8l6RHlCbhqSL8NiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"97","text":"3. Macro gestión (mecanismos de\\Npago, organización territorial):","guid":"ZlN9Xkir3_z6hJ1LOluM9A","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Pago por desempeño\\N(P4P), GRD´s.","guid":"tetIBtWn4f96GgwsYKU9rQ","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Problemas de inducción de\\Ndemanda y gasto de bolsillo.","guid":"15Slo4K896mTY-X94OHJ6w","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"Conclusiones","guid":"f2d_3QLXWILg7i9KC5lyLA","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Creciente preocupación en\\Npaíses de altos ingresos:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"• Investigación sobre el derroche en salud →\\Nevidencia para estrategias de contención de gasto.","guid":"gOj5pa35M_IVMrOgJEh4_A","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"• Mitigación del derroche = políticas, programas y\\Nprácticas basadas en evidencia científica.","guid":"wnLoEUWN6JY3pen-fGaHPQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"• Principales causales\\Ndel derroche:","guid":"XqwnTC-ri5uEl_nxKBr5OQ","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"• Uso innecesario de procedimientos\\Ndiagnósticos y terapéuticos.","guid":"eWYE6TB9_xQ3CYbk6teH5Q","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"• Uso inadecuado de medicamentos → baja\\Nadherencia en enfermedades crónicas.","guid":"6alJhUaoKXBJZOD8N6-xrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"108","text":"• Impacto de la formación\\Nde profesionales:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"• Necesidad de ajustes curriculares → mayor conciencia\\Ndel impacto económico de acciones clínicas.","guid":"e_xu-YmqG9nIW5oHf5VlSg","children":[]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"108","text":"• Escasez de estudios en\\NLatinoamérica y África:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"• Urgencia de cuantificar el derroche y\\Nexplorar factores causales.","guid":"bnYY0g2dD5V6aXA2U10NEQ","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"117","text":"• Futuros estudios necesarios para mejorar la eficiencia\\Ny equidad en los sistemas de salud regionales.","guid":"oxBjJJBtq6ZFIQ99mOZR4w","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":119,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Gestión en salud","filename":"- Derroche en salud-2024","id":"map_1017","resolved_references":[]}